@node Shareware "VoiceShell shareware fee"
@prev Future
@next Source

@{u}SHAREWARE FEE@{uu}

As of version 1.01 @{b}VoiceShell@{ub} is @{u}ShareWare@{uu}. I am not hoping for a huge
amount of money, so I hope I will get some response. The fee is only $5 to
$10 (USD), or whatever that happens to make at the moment you're reading
this, in german marks (DM). If you're from Finland a sum of 20 FIM to 50
FIM would be great. I also accept postcards and EMail!
@endnode

